title: Jumpstart Music Learning Homeschool Educational
description:
CLICK ON MY NAME (CEZEN) TO SEE A COMPLETE LIST OF MY HOMESCHOOL AND EDUCATIONAL TORRENTS

Program from Jumpstart to teach the basics of music.  It teaches rythem and has the children pick out the "wrong" notes in a piece of music after having listened to it.  It is not difficult, it is appx 4 measures of music and also has the notes on a staff!  IT is a great beginning exposure to music for the homeschooling family who has NO musical background....

Use Ultra ISO (or your preferred software) and mount to virtual drive and use OR burn to cd.  No serial keys etc required... ENJOY
